Metric: Budget Utilization (Excel)
Description: Total dollars spent against budget across all departments, read from a Finance-owned spreadsheet. The "Finance emails you an xlsx every Monday" scenario.
Owner: demo
Tags: demo, excel, finance

Source: budget

Given all records from the budget table
  And budgeted is present
  And spent is present

When we calculate
  Then sum the spent column across all rows

The result is "Budget Utilization"

Trust:
  Freshness must be less than 72 hours
  Null rate on spent must be 0%
  Null rate on budgeted must be 0%
  Value must be between 100000 and 10000000
